    "title": "Kanisa",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "kanisa",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kanisa ni jumuiya ya watu wanaomtambua Kristo kama Bwana na kumtii (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:21-Eph5:24\">Waefeso 5:21–24</a>). Neno la Agano Jipya kwa &quot;kanisa&quot; linatokana na neno la Kigiriki <em>ekklēsia</em> (linalomaanisha &quot;kikundi cha watu wanaokusanyika pamoja&quot;). Katika ulimwengu unaozungumza Kigiriki, neno hili lilitumika kwa aina mbalimbali za mikutano. Linaweza kumaanisha mkutano rasmi wa kisiasa au mkusanyiko usio rasmi wa watu (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:32\">Matendo 19:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:39\">39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:41\">41</a>). Katika Septuagint (tafsiri ya Kigiriki ya Agano la Kale), neno hili linarejelea wakati jumuiya ya Israeli ilipokutana (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:30\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 31:30</a>).</p><p>Kwenye Agano Jipya, <em>ekklēsia</em> inahusu:</p><ol><li><p>Mwili mzima wa Kristo duniani kote (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:18\">Mathayo 16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:22\">Waefeso 1:22</a>)</p></li><li><p>Wakristo wote katika eneo fulani (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:31\">Matendo 9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:2\">1 Wakorintho 1:2</a>)</p></li><li><p>Jumuiya ya eneo inayokutana mara kwa mara kwa ajili ya ibada, mafundisho, ushirika, na maombi (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:5\">Warumi 16:5</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:42\">Matendo 2:42</a>)</p></li></ol><p>Agano Jipya linatumia dhana kadhaa kuelezea kanisa:</p><ol><li><p><em>Waisraeli wa Mungu </em>(<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:16\">Wagalatia 6:16</a>): Wale ambao ni &quot;milki ya Mungu mwenyewe&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9-1Pet2:10\">1 Petro 2:9–10</a>). Wanatumikia kama “ukuhani mtakatifu, wakitoa dhabihu za kiroho zinazokubalika kwa Mungu&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:5\">1 Petro 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">9</a>).</p></li><li><p><em>Familia ya Mungu </em>(<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:19\">Waefeso 2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:15\">1 Timotheo 3:15</a>): Hii inajumuisha wale ambao wamepokelewa kama watoto wa kiroho wa Mungu na kuitwa warithi wake.</p></li><li><p><em>Hekalu takatifu</em>: Ni mahali ambapo Mungu anaishi kwa Roho wake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:21-Eph2:22\">Waefeso 2:21–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:6\">4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:16-1Cor3:17\">1 Wakorintho 3:16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:16\">2 Wakorintho 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:27\">Wakolosai 1:27</a>).</p></li><li><p><em>Mwili wa Kristo</em>: Wanamwakilisha Kristo kikamilifu duniani, na Kristo kama kiongozi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:23\">Waefeso 1:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:15\">4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:23-Eph5:24\">5:23–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:12-1Cor12:27\">1 Wakorintho 12:12–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:18\">Wakolosai 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:24\">24</a>).</p></li><li><p><em>Bibi arusi safi wa Kristo</em>: Yule ambaye alikufa kwa ajili yake, anamtunza na kumthamini. Ataishi naye milele katika umoja. (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25-Eph5:29\">Waefeso 5:25–29</a>).</p></li></ol><p>Kanisa ni sehemu ya mpango wa Mungu wa kuunganisha kila kitu mbinguni na duniani chini ya mamlaka ya Kristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:9-Eph1:10\">Waefeso 1:9–10</a>). Kupitia Yesu Kristo, Mungu amewaita watu kutoka Uyahudi na mataifa mengine kuwa watu wapya wa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:16\">Wagalatia 6:16</a>). Wanawezeshwa na Roho wake kuwa na uwepo duniani, kumwabudu, na kushiriki habari njema (injili) ya upendo wake usio na masharti (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:11-Eph2:22\">Waefeso 2:11–22</a>).</p><p>Mizizi ya kiroho ya kanisa yapo katika Uyahudi. Kanisa linatimiza kusudi la Mungu kwa Israeli kuwa &quot;nuru kwa mataifa&quot; na &quot;kuleta wokovu Wangu hadi miisho ya dunia&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:6\">Isaya 49:6</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:1-Rom11:5\">Warumi 11:1–5</a>). Katika jamii hii mpya ya waumini wa Kiyahudi na wasio wa Kiyahudi, Yesu anavunja mgawanyiko wote wa zamani kati ya watu. Hakuna anayechukuliwa kuwa bora au mbaya zaidi kuliko wengine kwa sababu ya asili yao ya kikabila, nafasi ya kijamii, au kama ni mwanamume au mwanamke (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:28\">Wagalatia 3:28</a>).</p><p>Wale walio unganishwa na Kristo ni washiriki wa mwili wake. Paulo anaelezea uhusiano wa karibu kati ya Kristo na watu wake kuwa sawa na umoja wa mwili wa kimwili (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:4-Rom12:8\">Warumi 12:4–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:12-1Cor12:27\">1 Wakorintho 12:12–27</a>). Kuwa &quot;katika Kristo&quot; kunamaanisha &quot;kubatizwa katika mwili mmoja&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:12-1Cor12:13\">1 Wakorintho 12:12–13</a>). Kwa hiyo, &quot;ninyi ni mwili wa Kristo, na kila mmoja wenu ni mshiriki wake&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:27\">1 Wakorintho 12:27</a>).</p><p>Wakristo wanaungana na Mungu kama sehemu ya familia mpya. Kuwa &quot;katika Kristo&quot; kunamaanisha kuwa sehemu ya kanisa. Kuwa Mkristo kunamaanisha kujiunga na jamii inayojitolea kuonyesha uhalisi wa Kristo katika maisha yao ya pamoja.</p><p>Kama vile kanisa ni mwili mmoja, umoja ni muhimu. Paulo mara nyingi aliwahimiza Wakristo kudumisha umoja na kuepuka kuruhusu tofauti kuwatenganisha.</p><p>Kanisa linajumuisha watu kutoka makabila mbalimbali, hivyo linapaswa kuwa jamii ya maelewano na amani. Wakristo wanapaswa kuishi pamoja kwa upendo, wakiunganishwa na uzoefu wao wa pamoja wa Roho Mtakatifu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:2-Eph4:6\">Waefeso 4:2–6</a>). Lengo la Mungu kwa kanisa ni kufikia umoja kamili, imani, ufahamu wa kiroho, na ukomavu wa Kikristo. Anakusudia ukamilifu wa Kristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:13\">4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:15\">15</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">Warumi 8:29</a>). Kanisa lazima lionyeshe mfano wa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:24\">Waefeso 4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:32\">32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:1\">5:1</a>).</p><p>Kama vile kila sehemu ya mwili wa binadamu una jukumu lake, kila mshiriki wa kanisa ana kazi yake. Mungu amewapa watu katika kanisa vipawa mbalimbali ili kuimarisha jamii na kusaidia kufikia uwezo wake kamili (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:11-Eph4:16\">Waefeso 4:11–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:6-Rom12:8\">Warumi 12:6–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:7-1Cor12:11\">1 Wakorintho 12:7–11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:28\">28</a>).</p><p>Mungu anakusudia kanisa lionyeshe neema yake ya kusamehe (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:7\">Waefeso 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:10\">3:10</a>). Kanisa linapaswa kuwa jamii ambapo watu wanaweza kuuona utukufu wa Mungu na kujitolea kuusifu utukufu huo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:21\">3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:18-Eph5:20\">5:18–20</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">Warumi 8:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:6-Rom12:8\">12:6–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:16-1Cor3:17\">1 Wakorintho 3:16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:16\">6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:7-1Cor12:28\">12:7–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:16\">Wagalatia 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:9-Eph1:10\">Waefeso 1:9–10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:23\">23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:7\">2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:14-Eph3:13\">2:14–3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:2-Eph4:6\">4:2–6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:11-Eph4:16\">11–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:18-Eph5:20\">5:18–20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:23-Eph5:29\">23–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:18\">Wakolosai 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:24\">24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:27\">27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:15\">1 Timotheo 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:5\">1 Petro 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9-1Pet2:10\">9–10</a></p>",
